original_title: UFC Fight Night 35: Rockhold vs. Philippou
overview: UFC Fight Night 35: Rockhold vs. Philippou was a mixed martial arts event held on January 15, 2014 at The Arena at Gwinnett Center in Duluth, Georgia. The event was headlined by a middleweight bout between Luke Rockhold and Costas Philippou.
title: UFC Fight Night 35: Rockhold vs. Philippou
